---

## 🎯 Key Objectives

- Turn layoffs into divine callings  
- Transform developers into gospel-aligned civic engineers  
- Establish a scalable, ethical deployment model across global cities

---

## 📚 Execution Phases

### ✅ Phase 1: Gateway Design (0–6 months)
- Build intake criteria (technical experience + ethical alignment)
- Launch UoPeople scholarship path
- Distribute Sanggi Park’s civic architecture materials

### ✅ Phase 2: Re-Alignment Training (6–18 months)
- Enroll in UoPeople (Business / CS / Health Science)
- Engage with GPT tutoring + gospel lectures + Doldol modules
- Complete Capstone: “Design a Gospel-Aligned City System”

### ✅ Phase 3: Global Deployment (18–36 months)
- Placement into Doldol Group's welfare, legal, educational, logistics roles
- Relocate to standard cities in Asia, Africa, Latin America
- Optional soft-landing citizenship support via National Alignment Bureau

